_json.description: PHOENIX CFA ROSE - MODERN SHRUB Rose Glorious blooms loaded with petals and fragrance - the colour is pale salmon pink with apricot and varies considerably as the rose opens from the bud to full bloom - a wonderful modern shrub rose which requires 1.5 metres of space for it so spread and branch with stems loaded with heavy blooms - beautiful rose named by CFA to commemorate 'rising from the ashes' after Black Saturday bushfires ravaged Victoria. $21.50
